
PICKED TASKS

* implement case statements
  * CASE expr_opt
  		WHEN expr THEN expr
  		...
  		ELSE expr -> if ELSE not present it is taken as NULL
  	END
  * SQL_CASE type sql_expression
  * {
  		sql_expression* case_expr; // may be NULL, if absent
  		arraylist when_exprs;
  		arraylist then_exprs;
  		sql_expression* else_expr; // may be NULL, if absent
  }

* add %destructor rules
%destructor { free($$); } non_terminal/terminal
%destructor { delete_temp($$); } unioned_type


